OL,3,C'Reckless and dangerous' driver jailed
OL,4,Cafter 30-minute police chase
OL,6,FThe moment police caught up with a man
OL,7,Fand tasered him following a 30-minute
OL,8,Fpolice pursuit in Bristol has been
OL,9,Fcaptured on camera.
OL,11,FBryan Smith reached speeds of 80mph in
OL,12,Fa 30mph zone, drove on pavements, and
OL,13,Fjumped several red lights through
OL,14,Fresidential areas of the city before
OL,15,Fofficers finally caught up with him in
OL,16,FFishponds.
OL,18,FThe 47-year-old was arrested by Avon
OL,19,Fand Somerset Police after he tried to
OL,20,Fforce his way through two black
OL,21,FRenault vehicles on Ledbury Road.
