OL,3,C'Reckless and dangerous' driver jailed
OL,4,Cafter 30-minute police chase
OL,6,FSmith admitted multiple driving
OL,7,Foffences and was jailed for 16 months
OL,8,Ffollowing a sentencing hearing at
OL,9,FBristol Crown Court on Thursday 9
OL,10,FOctober.
OL,12,FPolice Constable Dan Hamblin from the
OL,13,FAvon and Somerset Police Roads
OL,14,FPolicing Unit said Smith's driving
OL,15,Fcould have had "serious consequences."
OL,17,F"Smith's driving was amongst the most
OL,18,Freckless and exceedingly dangerous I
OL,19,Fhave ever seen," he said.
