OL,3,C'Reckless and dangerous' driver jailed
OL,4,Cafter 30-minute police chase
OL,6,F"Thanks to the skill of officers and
OL,7,Fthe support of the police helicopter,
OL,8,Fhe was stopped without anyone coming
OL,9,Fto harm.
OL,11,FThe court heard that on Tuesday 2
OL,12,FSeptember, officers spotted a car that
OL,13,Fhad been reported stolen a few days
OL,14,Fearlier and was being driven on cloned
OL,15,Fregistration plates.
OL,17,FOfficers attempted to stop Smith, but
OL,18,Fhe drove off at speed and led police
OL,19,Fon a 27-minute pursuit around southern
OL,20,Fand central Bristol.
