OL,3,C'Reckless and dangerous' driver jailed
OL,4,Cafter 30-minute police chase
OL,6,FThe court heard he drove onto
OL,7,Fpavements and went through red lights
OL,8,Fon multiple occasions before he
OL,9,Feventually became jammed between two
OL,10,Fvehicles belonging to members of the
OL,11,Fpublic.
OL,13,FOfficers attempting to arrest Smith
OL,14,Fspotted that he was still trying to
OL,15,Fdrive off despite the collision and
OL,16,Ftasered him to prevent the pursuit
OL,17,Ffrom continuing.
