OL,3,C'Reckless and dangerous' driver jailed
OL,4,Cafter 30-minute police chase
OL,6,FSmith pleaded guilty to four charges -
OL,7,Fdriving while disqualified, driving
OL,8,Fwithout insurance, failing to provide
OL,9,Fa specimen for analysis and dangerous
OL,10,Fdriving - when he appeared at Bristol
OL,11,FMagistrates Court.
OL,13,FHe was sentenced to 16 months in
OL,14,Fprison and was disqualified from
OL,15,Fdriving for 10 years and eight months.
OL,17,FPC Hamblin added: "Driving at the
OL,18,Fspeed and the manner he did could have
OL,19,Fhad serious consequences, and this
OL,20,Fsentence protects the public from him."
